txt.en: 'You have completed the battle at the gate!'
Are you prepared to leave the field of battle?

One of the Nine known to mortals as The Gloom of Nurn has emerged to answer your challenge at the gates of Dol Guldur. You and your allies must gather all of your strength if you have any hope of defeating him and his forces.
Defeat the Gloom of Nurn and his forces before the gates of Dol Guldur.
